Tale of the Forbidden Forest

It was 11:58 in the Forest of the Doomed. All anyone knows of this forest, is that no one ever comes out. Timmy, a young boy, decides to find out. Entering the forest, there are rumbles on the ground, an Timmy finds a cave. He see's a rotting helmet on the ground, knowing it is from a soldier. He hears a cry in the cave. As he gets closer, he makes out the cry... 
DEMAGLIO {{champion:150}}

